00:00:06.361 --> 00:00:10.813
today we will prepare bathua raita made especially during winters.

00:00:11.118 --> 00:00:16.602
let's see what all ingerdients are required for making bathua raita.

00:00:17.110 --> 00:00:20.015
bathua - 200 grams (leaves)

00:00:20.343 --> 00:00:21.954
curd - 2 cup

00:00:22.774 --> 00:00:27.389
plain salt - 1/4 tsp or as per taste

00:00:27.995 --> 00:00:30.447
green chilly -1 (finely chopped)

00:00:30.736 --> 00:00:32.450
ghee - 1 tsp

00:00:32.897 --> 00:00:34.381
asafoetida- 1 pinch

00:00:34.661 --> 00:00:36.502
cumin seeds - 1/2 tsp

00:00:36.766 --> 00:00:38.877
black salt - 1/4 tsp

00:00:39.364 --> 00:00:43.062
boil bathua first for making raita.

00:00:43.351 --> 00:00:50.307
we have alreadt cleaned,washed and dried bathua.

00:01:06.986 --> 00:01:14.593
add some water,cover and cook for 5-6 minutes.

00:01:16.850 --> 00:01:19.431
bathua is rady,turn off the gas.

00:01:19.711 --> 00:01:24.945
drain out excess water and after it gets frigid grind to make paste.

00:01:29.939 --> 00:01:36.336
we have grinded the bathua,make sure to don't grind it too finely.

00:01:37.168 --> 00:01:56.296
we have already whisked curd,add bathua paste,salt,balck salt and green chilly into it.

00:01:58.223 --> 00:02:00.286
mix all ingredients.

00:02:05.404 --> 00:02:07.984
now add tadka into it.

00:02:08.535 --> 00:02:21.762
add ghee,asafoetida and cumin seeds in preheated pan.

00:02:24.280 --> 00:02:32.382
when cumin seeds turn little brown add tadka in raita.

00:02:38.725 --> 00:02:43.677
you can also roast cumin seeds-asafoetida on tawa first,grind them and then add in curd.

00:02:56.244 --> 00:02:58.038
bathua raita is ready.

